title: Multi-vehicle accident with tractor-trailer on its side creates delays on Interstate 78 | PHOTOS – The Morning Call

Multi-vehicle accident with tractor-trailer on its side creates delays on Interstate 78 | PHOTOS By Rich Rolen | Special to The Morning Call PUBLISHED: December 28, 2023 at 5:29 p.m. | UPDATED: December 28, 2023 at 5:30 p.m. A multi-vehicle accident on Interstate 78 eastbound in Upper Saucon Township creates delays.
A tractor-trailer lies on its side after rolling over in a multivehicle accident Thursday, Dec. 28, 2023, on Interstate 78 eastbound in Upper Saucon Township.
